text: Chiswick is a suburb in London, England. The name may also refer to: *Chiswick, New South Wales, a suburb of Sydney, Australia *Chiswick House, a Palladian villa in Chiswick, London *Lord Chiswick, a character from the 1983–1989 British sitcom Blackadder *Chiswick Records, an English record label 1975–1983 ==See also== *Cheswick (disambiguation)
